{
  "8LWpeBX6ZwY": [
    {
      "text": "This is the Coalition Emergency",
      "start": 4.8,
      "duration": 4.64
    },
    {
      "text": "Broadcast System.",
      "start": 6.32,
      "duration": 3.12
    },
    {
      "text": "There are reports of multiple tremors",
      "start": 10,
      "duration": 5.8
    },
    {
      "text": "causing minor damage across Colona.",
      "start": 11.76,
      "duration": 4.04
    },
    {
      "text": ">> Stay sharp. Don't let them surround you.",
      "start": 18.56,
      "duration": 4.2
    },
    {
      "text": ">> There should be more guns in the trunk.",
      "start": 24.04,
      "duration": 6.72
    },
    {
      "text": ">> Here. Strap these on.",
      "start": 27.2,
      "duration": 3.56
    },
    {
      "text": ">> This isn't enough.",
      "start": 33.04,
      "duration": 3.52
    },
    {
      "text": "We should still head to the police",
      "start": 35.68,
      "duration": 2
    },
    {
      "text": "station.",
      "start": 36.56,
      "duration": 2
    },
    {
      "text": "We're going to have more firepower",
      "start": 37.68,
      "duration": 1.24
    },
    {
      "text": "there.",
      "start": 38.56,
      "duration": 1.16
    },
    {
      "text": ">> Right.",
      "start": 38.92,
      "duration": 1.6
    },
    {
      "text": ">> Yeah.",
      "start": 39.72,
      "duration": 2.76
    },
    {
      "text": ">> It's about two blocks up ahead.",
      "start": 40.52,
      "duration": 3
    },
    {
      "text": ">> Okay.",
      "start": 42.48,
      "duration": 1.56
    },
    {
      "text": ">> Come on.",
      "start": 43.52,
      "duration": 4.48
    },
    {
      "text": ">> Shoot, move, AND WATCH FOR CIVILIANS.",
      "start": 44.04,
      "duration": 3.96
    },
    {
      "text": "GET inside now.",
      "start": 51.44,
      "duration": 3.44
    },
    {
      "text": ">> [screaming]",
      "start": 58.295,
      "duration": 4.825
    },
    {
      "text": ">> Ground's opening.",
      "start": 60.12,
      "duration": 3
    },
    {
      "text": ">> There's too many.",
      "start": 78.32,
      "duration": 2.64
    },
    {
      "text": "Henry!",
      "start": 82.56,
      "duration": 3.245
    },
    {
      "text": "Henry, where are you?",
      "start": 83.4,
      "duration": 4.425
    },
    {
      "text": ">> [screaming]",
      "start": 85.805,
      "duration": 2.02
    },
    {
      "text": ">> You see that?",
      "start": 102,
      "duration": 3
    },
    {
      "text": "It was something big.",
      "start": 103.44,
      "duration": 3.36
    },
    {
      "text": "Like huge track fingers digging up",
      "start": 105,
      "duration": 3.36
    },
    {
      "text": "through the street.",
      "start": 106.8,
      "duration": 3.44
    },
    {
      "text": "Just the adrenaline hit.",
      "start": 108.36,
      "duration": 3.24
    },
    {
      "text": "We need to keep moving. Through the",
      "start": 110.24,
      "duration": 3.4
    },
    {
      "text": "underpass.",
      "start": 111.6,
      "duration": 5.12
    },
    {
      "text": ">> Let's get moving.",
      "start": 113.64,
      "duration": 3.08
    },
    {
      "text": ">> Let me see what I can do.",
      "start": 117.24,
      "duration": 3.08
    },
    {
      "text": ">> I'm at the Pay 'n' Save. I need backup.",
      "start": 120.76,
      "duration": 4.08
    },
    {
      "text": "These things are all over me.",
      "start": 125,
      "duration": 3.759
    },
    {
      "text": ">> More tremors.",
      "start": 127.32,
      "duration": 2.84
    },
    {
      "text": ">> Any Gears out there, anyone that can",
      "start": 128.759,
      "duration": 3.92
    },
    {
      "text": "hear this?",
      "start": 130.16,
      "duration": 2.519
    },
    {
      "text": "Look out!",
      "start": 140.52,
      "duration": 2.6
    },
    {
      "text": ">> Oh, [ __ ]",
      "start": 140.92,
      "duration": 5.039
    },
    {
      "text": "What the [ __ ] IS THAT?",
      "start": 143.12,
      "duration": 2.839
    },
    {
      "text": ">> TARGET SIGHTED. OPEN FIRE.",
      "start": 148.12,
      "duration": 3.92
    },
    {
      "text": ">> THESE ARE GODDAMN breach points.",
      "start": 162.88,
      "duration": 3.6
    },
    {
      "text": ">> Reloading. Cover me.",
      "start": 173.52,
      "duration": 3.24
    },
    {
      "text": ">> [screaming]",
      "start": 180.127,
      "duration": 2.02
    },
    {
      "text": "[groaning]",
      "start": 182.747,
      "duration": 2.02
    },
    {
      "text": ">> All right.",
      "start": 185.44,
      "duration": 2.96
    },
    {
      "text": "That Gear said they're stuck in the Pay",
      "start": 186.84,
      "duration": 3.52
    },
    {
      "text": "'n' Save.",
      "start": 188.4,
      "duration": 3.32
    },
    {
      "text": "Which way?",
      "start": 190.36,
      "duration": 2.32
    },
    {
      "text": ">> It's on the other side of those",
      "start": 191.72,
      "duration": 2.92
    },
    {
      "text": "apartments.",
      "start": 192.68,
      "duration": 2.92
    },
    {
      "text": "At least that thing [music] carved us a",
      "start": 194.64,
      "duration": 3.56
    },
    {
      "text": "shortcut.",
      "start": 195.6,
      "duration": 2.6
    },
    {
      "text": ">> Through here.",
      "start": 198.32,
      "duration": 2.76
    },
    {
      "text": ">> Who's there?",
      "start": 204.84,
      "duration": 2.64
    },
    {
      "text": "AH, BUGGER.",
      "start": 209.4,
      "duration": 4.04
    },
    {
      "text": "COME ON, MAN.",
      "start": 210.92,
      "duration": 2.52
    },
    {
      "text": "What the hell?",
      "start": 214.16,
      "duration": 3.68
    },
    {
      "text": "Oh.",
      "start": 216.239,
      "duration": 3.28
    },
    {
      "text": "Nice shot.",
      "start": 217.84,
      "duration": 3.44
    },
    {
      "text": "Oh. Where the hell did you lot come",
      "start": 219.519,
      "duration": 3.121
    },
    {
      "text": "from?",
      "start": 221.28,
      "duration": 3.12
    },
    {
      "text": ">> We heard your distress call.",
      "start": 222.64,
      "duration": 3.36
    },
    {
      "text": ">> Well, you saved my ass.",
      "start": 224.4,
      "duration": 3.68
    },
    {
      "text": "But we need to make ourselves scarce.",
      "start": 226,
      "duration": 3.959
    },
    {
      "text": "These [ __ ] keep pouring in every few",
      "start": 228.08,
      "duration": 4.28
    },
    {
      "text": "minutes.",
      "start": 229.959,
      "duration": 2.401
    },
    {
      "text": "More tremors.",
      "start": 234.4,
      "duration": 1.84
    },
    {
      "text": ">> Watch it.",
      "start": 235.08,
      "duration": 3.8
    },
    {
      "text": ">> RIGHT ON SCHEDULE.",
      "start": 236.24,
      "duration": 4.16
    },
    {
      "text": "YOU GUYS HERE?",
      "start": 238.88,
      "duration": 3.6
    },
    {
      "text": ">> YEAH. Who are you?",
      "start": 240.4,
      "duration": 4.4
    },
    {
      "text": ">> I'M WITH THE MILITIA.",
      "start": 242.48,
      "duration": 3.88
    },
    {
      "text": ">> WHERE'S YOUR SQUAD?",
      "start": 244.8,
      "duration": 3.64
    },
    {
      "text": ">> They sent me to scout out THE SWARM",
      "start": 246.36,
      "duration": 3.36
    },
    {
      "text": "OF MONSTERS.",
      "start": 248.44,
      "duration": 2.88
    },
    {
      "text": "WE WERE PROTECTING SOME survivors",
      "start": 249.72,
      "duration": 3.04
    },
    {
      "text": "nearby.",
      "start": 251.32,
      "duration": 3.12
    },
    {
      "text": "I'm about to get back to the corner of",
      "start": 252.76,
      "duration": 3.88
    },
    {
      "text": "the hill.",
      "start": 254.44,
      "duration": 2.2
    },
    {
      "text": ">> [groaning]",
      "start": 263.312,
      "duration": 3.688
    },
    {
      "text": ">> Reloading. Cover.",
      "start": 263.919,
      "duration": 3.081
    },
    {
      "text": ">> Take tomorrow. These things been coming",
      "start": 268.52,
      "duration": 3.36
    },
    {
      "text": "in waves.",
      "start": 270.64,
      "duration": 1.92
    },
    {
      "text": ">> Ah,",
      "start": 271.88,
      "duration": 3.039
    },
    {
      "text": "I got a problem cuz I ran out of ammo.",
      "start": 272.56,
      "duration": 4.24
    },
    {
      "text": "I'm loading heavy artillery.",
      "start": 274.919,
      "duration": 4.881
    },
    {
      "text": "I got friends on my side.",
      "start": 276.8,
      "duration": 3
    },
    {
      "text": ">> [groaning]",
      "start": 284.928,
      "duration": 2.02
    },
    {
      "text": "[groaning and screaming]",
      "start": 289.513,
      "duration": 2.487
    },
    {
      "text": ">> Eat that.",
      "start": 290.6,
      "duration": 3.2
    },
    {
      "text": ">> Nah.",
      "start": 292,
      "duration": 4.64
    },
    {
      "text": ">> Throwing a grenade.",
      "start": 293.8,
      "duration": 2.84
    },
    {
      "text": ">> They come.",
      "start": 297.76,
      "duration": 3.44
    },
    {
      "text": "Watch your back.",
      "start": 298.76,
      "duration": 2.44
    },
    {
      "text": ">> RELOADING.",
      "start": 304,
      "duration": 2.88
    },
    {
      "text": ">> DIE.",
      "start": 310.48,
      "duration": 2.28
    },
    {
      "text": ">> GOT TO RELOAD.",
      "start": 317.32,
      "duration": 2.56
    },
    {
      "text": ">> ANYONE SEE HIM?",
      "start": 320.2,
      "duration": 3
    },
    {
      "text": ">> CONTACT FRONT.",
      "start": 323.72,
      "duration": 5.48
    },
    {
      "text": ">> THERE'S NO END TO THESE FREAKS.",
      "start": 325.919,
      "duration": 3.281
    },
    {
      "text": ">> PICK THEM OFF.",
      "start": 337.44,
      "duration": 4.12
    },
    {
      "text": ">> ON YOUR RIGHT, PARTNER.",
      "start": 339.88,
      "duration": 4.24
    },
    {
      "text": ">> I got it.",
      "start": 341.56,
      "duration": 2.56
    },
    {
      "text": ">> Jammed.",
      "start": 347.32,
      "duration": 2.48
    },
    {
      "text": ">> DAMN IT.",
      "start": 348.44,
      "duration": 1.988
    },
    {
      "text": ">> HEY.",
      "start": 349.8,
      "duration": 2.648
    },
    {
      "text": ">> [screaming]",
      "start": 350.428,
      "duration": 2.02
    },
    {
      "text": "[groaning]",
      "start": 362.219,
      "duration": 2.02
    },
    {
      "text": "[screaming]",
      "start": 368.769,
      "duration": 2.02
    },
    {
      "text": "[groaning]",
      "start": 372.044,
      "duration": 2.356
    },
    {
      "text": ">> DOM.",
      "start": 373.2,
      "duration": 3.2
    },
    {
      "text": ">> I'M ALMOST THERE.",
      "start": 374.4,
      "duration": 4.28
    },
    {
      "text": "I'M almost there.",
      "start": 376.4,
      "duration": 2.28
    },
    {
      "text": ">> [groaning]",
      "start": 387.109,
      "duration": 2.02
    },
    {
      "text": ">> Our roads converge again.",
      "start": 392.64,
      "duration": 3.44
    },
    {
      "text": "Marcus Fenix.",
      "start": 396.76,
      "duration": 3.12
    }
  ],
  "z1CWk2Ft884": [
    {
      "text": "I could get used to this. Feels like",
      "start": 10.719,
      "duration": 5.761
    },
    {
      "text": "we're miles away from the cast.",
      "start": 13.12,
      "duration": 5.76
    },
    {
      "text": ">> The army. They'll see our boat as soon",
      "start": 16.48,
      "duration": 4.559
    },
    {
      "text": "as they arrive.",
      "start": 18.88,
      "duration": 4.159
    },
    {
      "text": "What's our plan?",
      "start": 21.039,
      "duration": 3.761
    },
    {
      "text": "Well, we've got the book. We know the",
      "start": 23.039,
      "duration": 3.761
    },
    {
      "text": "island better than they do.",
      "start": 24.8,
      "duration": 5.04
    },
    {
      "text": ">> Oh, we're so close, Lenny. We can slip",
      "start": 26.8,
      "duration": 6.72
    },
    {
      "text": "away before they catch sight of us.",
      "start": 29.84,
      "duration": 5.68
    },
    {
      "text": "Believe me,",
      "start": 33.52,
      "duration": 4.879
    },
    {
      "text": "I can feel it. There's something on this",
      "start": 35.52,
      "duration": 5.879
    },
    {
      "text": "island.",
      "start": 38.399,
      "duration": 3
    },
    {
      "text": "I'm the key.",
      "start": 57.68,
      "duration": 3.84
    },
    {
      "text": ">> The thief's here, you as she's got the",
      "start": 59.359,
      "duration": 4.161
    },
    {
      "text": "sphere. If we catch her, we'll get a",
      "start": 61.52,
      "duration": 3.52
    },
    {
      "text": "better share of the loot.",
      "start": 63.52,
      "duration": 5.12
    },
    {
      "text": ">> U pirate.",
      "start": 65.04,
      "duration": 4.96
    },
    {
      "text": "Sort out.",
      "start": 68.64,
      "duration": 5.4
    },
    {
      "text": ">> Careful. You cut yourselves.",
      "start": 70,
      "duration": 4.04
    },
    {
      "text": "I'll make it sl",
      "start": 82.159,
      "duration": 3.64
    },
    {
      "text": "Are you hurt?",
      "start": 88.08,
      "duration": 7.079
    },
    {
      "text": "No. Let's move before more come.",
      "start": 89.92,
      "duration": 5.239
    },
    {
      "text": "The wave bird. What? Still thinking of a",
      "start": 101.52,
      "duration": 6.32
    },
    {
      "text": "name for our future boat. Is now the",
      "start": 105.28,
      "duration": 4.08
    },
    {
      "text": "right time?",
      "start": 107.84,
      "duration": 5.4
    },
    {
      "text": ">> It's never the right time.",
      "start": 109.36,
      "duration": 3.88
    },
    {
      "text": ">> Strange seeing everything the gang left",
      "start": 122.88,
      "duration": 3.199
    },
    {
      "text": "behind.",
      "start": 125.2,
      "duration": 4.919
    },
    {
      "text": ">> They thought they'd be back soon.",
      "start": 126.079,
      "duration": 4.04
    },
    {
      "text": "Jesus.",
      "start": 153.76,
      "duration": 4.4
    },
    {
      "text": ">> Cuz come at me.",
      "start": 155.12,
      "duration": 4.72
    },
    {
      "text": ">> Did you really think you could sneak in",
      "start": 158.16,
      "duration": 2.56
    },
    {
      "text": "like that?",
      "start": 159.84,
      "duration": 4.88
    },
    {
      "text": ">> Doesn't look like we tried to.",
      "start": 160.72,
      "duration": 4
    },
    {
      "text": "Shut this one up, sir.",
      "start": 169.04,
      "duration": 3.8
    },
    {
      "text": ">> I'll make sure you scream.",
      "start": 176.4,
      "duration": 4.199
    },
    {
      "text": "What happened here?",
      "start": 203.599,
      "duration": 3.801
    },
    {
      "text": "God, I didn't realize how big it was.",
      "start": 214.08,
      "duration": 5.159
    },
    {
      "text": "I should write these down.",
      "start": 223.92,
      "duration": 4.039
    },
    {
      "text": ">> What now?",
      "start": 235.68,
      "duration": 3.32
    },
    {
      "text": "I can use this to find our way through.",
      "start": 246.319,
      "duration": 4.441
    },
    {
      "text": "These were made of glass in the fresco",
      "start": 261.6,
      "duration": 3.599
    },
    {
      "text": "room, right? Must have been put here on",
      "start": 263.28,
      "duration": 4.919
    },
    {
      "text": "purpose.",
      "start": 265.199,
      "duration": 3
    },
    {
      "text": "Did they have to make everything so damn",
      "start": 283.36,
      "duration": 4.68
    },
    {
      "text": "complicated?",
      "start": 285.04,
      "duration": 3
    },
    {
      "text": "Holy hell.",
      "start": 298.32,
      "duration": 3.56
    },
    {
      "text": "Did they not have any sense of scale?",
      "start": 302.88,
      "duration": 6.28
    },
    {
      "text": "Clearly not.",
      "start": 305.68,
      "duration": 3.48
    },
    {
      "text": ">> This is",
      "start": 309.28,
      "duration": 3.16
    },
    {
      "text": "Heat. Heat.",
      "start": 341.28,
      "duration": 3.08
    },
    {
      "text": "Heat. Heat. Heat.",
      "start": 346.88,
      "duration": 3
    },
    {
      "text": "Where the hell am I?",
      "start": 383.28,
      "duration": 3.88
    },
    {
      "text": "Oh god,",
      "start": 398.16,
      "duration": 6.2
    },
    {
      "text": "I need to breathe.",
      "start": 400.8,
      "duration": 3.56
    },
    {
      "text": "Just a bit further.",
      "start": 413.759,
      "duration": 3.481
    },
    {
      "text": "the monster. It's not real.",
      "start": 424.08,
      "duration": 4.839
    }
  ],
  "Zv5kk_Ck65k": [
    {
      "text": "Akashima Island",
      "start": 8.2,
      "duration": 2.2
    },
    {
      "text": ">> [music]",
      "start": 9.825,
      "duration": 3.495
    },
    {
      "text": ">> haunted by dark stories.",
      "start": 10.4,
      "duration": 4.01
    },
    {
      "text": "Our goal",
      "start": 13.32,
      "duration": 1.32
    },
    {
      "text": ">> [music]",
      "start": 14.41,
      "duration": 3.67
    },
    {
      "text": ">> confront the evil corrupting paradise.",
      "start": 14.64,
      "duration": 4.72
    },
    {
      "text": "This is",
      "start": 18.08,
      "duration": 2.96
    },
    {
      "text": "Dead True",
      "start": 19.36,
      "duration": 4.52
    },
    {
      "text": "International.",
      "start": 21.04,
      "duration": 2.84
    },
    {
      "text": ">> [music]",
      "start": 28.82,
      "duration": 4.78
    },
    {
      "text": ">> Come on, let's get a photo together.",
      "start": 30.28,
      "duration": 3.32
    },
    {
      "text": ">> [music]",
      "start": 34.06,
      "duration": 2.02
    },
    {
      "text": ">> Over. Rotated on that one.",
      "start": 38.04,
      "duration": 4.48
    },
    {
      "text": ">> A for effort, dude. [music]",
      "start": 40.08,
      "duration": 3.92
    },
    {
      "text": ">> Who's the buff idiot?",
      "start": 42.52,
      "duration": 4.96
    },
    {
      "text": ">> Does no one know this guy?",
      "start": 44,
      "duration": 3.48
    },
    {
      "text": ">> [music]",
      "start": 51.745,
      "duration": 2.495
    },
    {
      "text": ">> Oh, you two haven't met yet, right?",
      "start": 52.04,
      "duration": 4.16
    },
    {
      "text": ">> Sebastian.",
      "start": 54.24,
      "duration": 4.76
    },
    {
      "text": "I've been looking out for you.",
      "start": 56.2,
      "duration": 2.8
    },
    {
      "text": "Roll whenever you're ready.",
      "start": 59.6,
      "duration": 2.56
    },
    {
      "text": ">> This facility [music]",
      "start": 61.36,
      "duration": 3.24
    },
    {
      "text": "has been shut down for decades.",
      "start": 62.16,
      "duration": 6.56
    },
    {
      "text": "Uninvestigated, untold until",
      "start": 64.6,
      "duration": 6.56
    },
    {
      "text": "now.",
      "start": 68.72,
      "duration": 2.44
    },
    {
      "text": ">> Did you hear that?",
      "start": 75.88,
      "duration": 2.76
    },
    {
